    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Business process of planning, developing, launching and managing a product or service. It covers the entire life cycle of a product, from conception to development and marketing. An important goal of product managment is ensuring that a product meets the needs of its target market and contributes to business strategy. The product manager manages a product or products through all phases of the product life cycle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
